    "The Moderation API is utilized to warn or block unsafe content, but false negatives and positives can occur.",
    "OpenAI seeks user feedback to enhance the system continually.",
    "The reader is invited to test ChatGPT by running the following three generic knowledge queries, for which ChatGPT produces answers of varying quality: (Correct answer) \"How Liz Taylor, Richard Burton, and John Hurt are related?",
